$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
repeat_event_person_say

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
repeat_event_person_say -  This is called on the repeater object to process the actual message event_person_say message.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void repeat_event_person_say(object caller,
object ob,
string start,
string mess,
string lang)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^caller%^RESET%^ - the repeater who sent the message
%^BOLD%^ob%^RESET%^ - the object that did the say
%^BOLD%^start%^RESET%^ - the start string
%^BOLD%^mess%^RESET%^ - the message string
%^BOLD%^lang%^RESET%^ - the language the message is in

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/repeater.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This is called on the repeater object to process the actual message
event_person_say message.
.EP

